graph TD
    %% Styles
    classDef process fill:#E67E22,stroke:#D35400,stroke-width:2px,color:#FFFFFF,rx:20,ry:20;
    classDef datastore fill:#27AE60,stroke:#2ECC71,stroke-width:2px,color:#FFFFFF;
    classDef io fill:#9B59B6,stroke:#8E44AD,stroke-width:2px,color:#FFFFFF;

    Input[/Raw Analog Sound\]:::io
    
    P1((1.0<br>Capture &<br>Digitize Audio)):::process
    P2((2.0<br>Extract Audio<br>Features)):::process
    P3((3.0<br>Execute TFLite<br>Inference)):::process
    P4((4.0<br>Analyze & Filter<br>Context)):::process
    P5((5.0<br>Dispatch Hardware<br>Alerts)):::process
    P6((6.0<br>Log Event<br>History)):::process

    D1[(D1: Smart Zone Settings)]:::datastore
    D2[(D2: Local Storage)]:::datastore
    
    Out1[/Vibration Output\]:::io
    Out2[/Visual Output\]:::io

    Input --> P1
    P1 -->|16kHz Digital Stream| P2
    P2 -->|Mel-Spectrogram Matrix| P3
    P3 -->|Array of 521 Class Scores| P4
    
    D1 -.->|Whitelist Rules| P4
    P4 -->|Filtered Positive Event| P5
    P4 -->|Filtered Positive Event| P6
    
    P5 -->|Haptic API Call| Out1
    P5 -->|Render / Flash API Call| Out2
    P6 -->|Save Event Log| D2
